Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.52,0:48:09.44,Upper Left Credit,,0,0,0,,Ómori: NAGACUKA KEIŠI\N\NMinami: KUROKI HARU
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.44,0:48:13.36,Upper Left Credit,,0,0,0,,KIIŠI JUKINO\NURABE FUSAKO\NIWATA RJÚMON
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.36,0:48:17.29,Upper Left Credit,,0,0,0,,HIRO-OKA JURIKO\NJOŠIOKA MUCUO\NNAKAZAWA AOROKU
